          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Bay and Stew began in 2013 when I first started making jewelry and couldn’t find high-quality stamping blanks that met my standards — so I began making my own. Soon after, I started offering these blanks to other small jewelry businesses, and from there, expanded into chains, findings, and more.</p><p>When permanent jewelry began to take off, I received more and more requests for my gold-filled connectors and custom hand-stamped pieces from customers in the permanent jewelry industry. </p>",
