            "text": "<h3>Today, Bay and Stew is proud to supply premium materials to makers across the handmade, engraved, and permanent jewelry communities.</h3><p>The name <em>Bay and Stew</em> comes from my two Italian Greyhounds, Bailey and Stewie, who were always by my side in the studio while I created jewelry. Though they’re no longer with me, their memory is a sweet reminder of where it all started — with passion, creativity, and a lot of heart.</p>",
